The paper deals with the modelling of biological systems using Markov population models, which are a type of stochastic process. This suggests that the paper is likely to fall under the category of "Logic in Computer Science" (cs.LO) or "Systems and Control" (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper uses continuous stochastic logic (CSL) to express properties of the models, which suggests that it could also fall under the category of "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI) or "Data Structures and Algorithms" (cs.DS). Finally, the paper deals specifically with biological systems, which suggests that it could also fall under the category of "Bioinformatics" (cs.BIO).
